  "title": "*URGENT* AGENCY ENROLLED/STAFF NURSES NEEDED!!! #HCGT",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>-         Providing excellent direct patient care and assistance</p><p>-         Assessing and monitoring patients’ conditions, taking vital signs, recording medical symptoms and histories, monitoring progress</p><p>-         Administering treatments and medications</p><p>-         Maintain accurate patient records</p><p>-          </p><p>Job Requirement:</p><p>-         NITEC/Diploma/Degree in Nursing</p><p>-         Minimum 2 years of experience</p><p>-         Available to start work immediately/on short notice period</p><p>-         Valid BCLS and SNB</p><p>All qualified applicants, please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>Tricia Celestine Goh (R1981653)<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No.199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>",
